files.name: README.md
files.content:
# Imagine

[![build](https://travis-ci.org/meowtec/Imagine.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/meowtec/Imagine)

Imagine is a desktop app for compression of PNG and JPEG, with a modern and friendly UI.

Save for web.

## Install

For Windows, macOS and Linux, download binaries from:

[https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine/releases](https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine/releases)

 - `Imagine-Setup-x.y.z.exe`      - *Windows*
 - `Imagine-x.y.z.dmg`            - *macOS*
 - `Imagine-0.4.1-x.y.z.AppImage` - *Linux*

国内用户从 GitHub 下载可能比较慢，可以使用[国内加速](https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine/issues/7)

### Install on linux

App for linux is distributed in [AppImage](http://appimage.org/) format.
Install it with command line:

```bash
chmod a+x Imagine-x.y.z-x86_64.AppImage # make executable
./Imagine-x.y.z-x86_64.AppImage # install and run
```

## Screenshot

![Screenshot](./screenshots/shot.jpg)

## Features

 - Multi format (JPEG, PNG, WebP)
 - Format conversion
 - Cross platform
 - GUI
 - Batch optimization
 - i18n (English, 简体中文, Nederlands, Español, Français, Italiano, Deutsch)

## Build and Contribute

```bash
git clone https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine.git
npm install
npm run dev
```

A PR with **all checks passed** is welcome.

Before submit a PR, please run `npm run test` and make sure it success on your machine.

Up to now, there are only [5 locales](https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine/tree/dev/modules/locales). To add a new locale, you can either submit a PR, or [create an issue](https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine/issues/new), or just send me an email(found in [my profile](https://github.com/meowtec)).

## Built on

 - [pngquant](https://pngquant.org/): Lossy PNG compressor
 - [mozjpeg](https://github.com/mozilla/mozjpeg): Improved JPEG encoder
 - [WebP](https://developers.google.com/speed/webp/): A new image format for the Web
 - [Electron](https://electron.atom.io/): Build cross platform desktop apps with JavaScript, HTML, and CSS

files.name: issue_template.md
files.content:
<!--
This is a template for bug submit.
If you are to request a new feature or for other purposes, clean the template.
-->

### Version
eg: 0.3.1

### Operating system (version and arch)
eg: Windows 10 x64

### Describe the bug
What happened?

### Screenshot

### Logs
<!--
The logs file is the following locations:

on Linux: ~/.config/imagine/log.log
on OS X: ~/Library/Logs/imagine/log.log
on Windows: %USERPROFILE%\AppData\Roaming\imagine\log.log
(%USERPROFILE% may be like \users\yourname)
-->

{
  "name": "Imagine",
  "private": true,
  "version": "0.7.5",
  "description": "PNG/JPEG optimization app",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/meowtec/Imagine.git"
  },
  "main": "./lib/bootstrap.js",
  "scripts": {
    "lint": "tsc --noEmit && eslint --ext .js,.jsx,.ts,.tsx modules",
    "tscw": "tsc -w",
    "dev": "tsc && cross-env IMAGINE_ENV=development electron .",
    "build": "rimraf lib dist && tsc && cross-env IMAGINE_ENV=production vite build",
    "start": "npm run build && electron .",
    "pack": "npm run build && electron-builder --dir",
    "release": "npm run build && electron-builder --publish always",
    "test": "tsc && npm run lint && jest"
  },
  "author": "meowtec<bertonzh@gmail.com>",
  "license": "ISC",
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/electron-devtools-installer": "~2.2.0",
    "@types/fs-extra": "^9.0.7",
    "@types/jest": "^27.4.0",
    "@types/lodash": "^4.14.168",
    "@types/pixelmatch": "^5.2.2",
    "@types/react": "^17.0.2",
    "@types/react-dom": "^17.0.1",
    "@types/react-redux": "^7.1.16",
    "@types/react-transition-group": "^4.4.1",
    "@types/react-window": "^1.8.2",
    "@types/redux-actions": "^2.6.1",
    "@types/semver": "^7.3.4",
    "@types/uuid": "^8.3.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^5.12.1",
    "@vitejs/plugin-react": "^1.3.2",
    "babel-core": "^6.26.3",
    "babel-loader": "^8.2.2",
    "classnames": "^2.2.6",
    "cross-env": "^7.0.3",
    "css-loader": "^6.6.0",
    "electron": "^12.2.3",
    "electron-builder": "^23.3.3",
    "electron-devtools-installer": "^3.1.1",
    "eslint": "^8.9.0",
    "eslint-config-airbnb": "^19.0.4",
    "eslint-config-airbnb-typescript": "^16.1.0",
    "eslint-plugin-import": "^2.22.1",
    "eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y": "^6.4.1",
    "eslint-plugin-react": "^7.22.0",
    "eslint-plugin-react-hooks": "^4.2.0",
    "eslint-plugin-unicorn": "^41.0.0",
    "jest": "^27.5.1",
    "less": "^4.1.1",
    "less-loader": "^10.2.0",
    "pixelmatch": "^5.2.1",
    "popper.js": "^1.16.1",
    "react": "^17.0.1",
    "react-dom": "^17.0.1",
    "react-redux": "^7.2.2",
    "react-refresh": "^0.11.0",
    "react-transition-group": "^4.4.1",
    "react-use": "^17.2.1",
    "react-window": "^1.8.6",
    "redux": "^4.0.5",
    "redux-actions": "^2.6.5",
    "reselect": "^4.0.0",
    "rimraf": "^3.0.2",
    "style-loader": "^3.3.1",
    "svg-sprite-loader": "^6.0.11",
    "ts-jest": "^27.1.3",
    "ts-loader": "^9.2.6",
    "ts-node": "^10.5.0",
    "typescript": "^4.2.2",
    "vite": "^2.9.14",
    "vite-plugin-svg-sprite": "^0.2.6"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "child-process-promise": "^2.2.1",
    "electron-log": "^4.3.2",
    "electron-updater": "^5.2.1",
    "file-type": "^16.5.3",
    "fs-extra": "^10.0.0",
    "jimp": "^0.16.1",
    "lodash": "^4.17.21",
    "raw-body": "^2.4.1",
    "tslib": "^2.1.0"
  },
  "build": {
    "files": [
      "index.html",
      "lib",
      "dist/web",
      "bin/${platform}/${arch}/**/*"
    ],
    "asarUnpack": [
      "bin"
    ],
    "appId": "com.meowtec.imagine.app",
    "mac": {
      "category": "public.app-category.graphics-design",
      "target": {
        "target": "dmg",
        "arch": [
          "x64",
          "arm64"
        ]
      }
    },
    "win": {
      "target": [
        {
          "target": "nsis",
          "arch": [
            "x64"
          ]
        },
        {
          "target": "portable",
          "arch": [
            "x64"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "linux": {
      "category": "Graphics",
      "publish": [
        "github"
      ],
      "target": [
        {
          "target": "snap",
          "arch": [
            "x64"
          ]
        },
        {
          "target": "appimage",
          "arch": [
            "x64"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "nsis": {
      "perMachine": true,
      "allowElevation": false
    },
    "fileAssociations": [
      {
        "role": "Editor",
        "ext": "png"
      },
      {
        "role": "Editor",
        "ext": "jpg"
      },
      {
        "role": "Editor",
        "ext": "jpeg"
      }
    ]
  }
}
